F.A.Q

The BUG report section is for just that submitting bug reports of an issue with the mod itself. From here on out if you post an issue with this mod or any in the future in the forums it will be ignored and deleted. This is because the forums are NOT for "hey your crap mod isn't working". :p This is to keep the forums clean and positive for all. 
For those using AFT, remember to put my follower ABOVE AFT in load order otherwise you will get errors and or Tamako not following you, and your PC, XBOX or PS4 melting in a watery mess. [/size][/color]
